<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Patea</author>
<hymn_number>184</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka damlai huihpi a beih tieng leh,
 Ei hukdampa mel deihum chu mutang ka
 Tichun, ka kipahna chul puo'na,
 A mela van pakcha chu lun zing ta'na

[V2]
 Aw hinna Thing, na bak nuoiah.
 Van a Angelte a leng ui,
 Aw, ziechun kei haw hung chawl kau,
 Israel tang thiengtho a chun.

[V3]
 2. Zie khawpi hawih ngai a ka kahna,
 Chun lungkham buoina thihna theih hi le chu
 Tatna thisan zala lungdeihte,
 Khawvela hin Aw, a na khen tang ka ting,

[V4]
 3. Chieh zel hitiu aw, Zion chate
 I nawplenna diu gam lopi a nai tai
 Tulai lungkham kah leh buoina hi,
 I kipahnau pakcha'n hung lun ngei ina.

[V5]
 4. Ti chun khawpi hawih ka tun tieng leh,
 Ka lenna gamthip lam hi nga ta puong ka
 Belam No leh A Lalchutphah chu,
 Etnawp maktak leh kipahna bukim na'ng.</lyrics>
<title>Aw Hinna Thing</title>
</song>